<center><table border=0><tr><td><center><H2><font face=arial>Gosh level 8, you must have seen a lot</font></H2></center>
<font face=arial size=2><b>Posted By:</b> <A HREF="/cgi-local/whois.cgi?Gilthad">Gilthad</a><br>
<b>Posted On:</b> 3:21 p.m. 10/5/1999<br>
<b>Subject:</b> Gosh level 8, you must have seen a lot<p>
<br><center><img src="http://www.everworld.net/images/datel.gif" width=46 height=22 border=0><img src="http://www.everworld.net/images/dateblnk.gif" width=100 height=22 border=0><img src="http://www.everworld.net/images/dater.gif" width=306 height=22 border=0></center><BR><P ALIGN=CENTER><b>In Reply To:</b> <A HREF="http://www.everworld.net/cgi-local/forum/rallos_zek.cgi?read=102" TARGET=_self>EQ (Boring!)</A> (Enigma)
</STRONG><FONT SIZE=2 color=#F4D99F FACE=arial>
<P>OK, here's a thought: If you don't like a game, don't play it. Obviously you've tried every avenue to have fun with the game, and it's boring you.

<P>&gt; The problem with EQ is in its combat engine,
<BR>&gt; frankly it sucks, it is all hack &
<BR>&gt; slash, I am at lvl 8 now & already
<BR>&gt; bored, damn! :(
<BR>&gt; The combat is lame, no thinking required
<BR>&gt; period, all you have to do is “/c” if the
<BR>&gt; reply is in blue or green then Auto-attack,
<BR>&gt; else just run away or gang up on the damn
<BR>&gt; thing.
<BR>&gt; No strategy, no tactics, no skill, no guts
<BR>&gt; absolutely nothing is required for this job,
<BR>&gt; hack & slash your way, all day until you
<BR>&gt; bore yourself to dead!
<BR>&gt; The game is cool at the beginning but will
<BR>&gt; get boring after a few levels, now wait
<BR>&gt; & see if you don't believe me!
<BR>
</FONT></td></tr></table></P>
